{
  "stem": "27507.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew if they were coming, or if they were not coming, and what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But next morning, after we were waiting, and crawling out of the-- or looking out of the window, and out of the balconies, crawling into the balcony to see if they-- because there was nobody in the street.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was all empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we saw, suddenly, groups of people coming back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came back at maybe 11:00 o'clock, next day, after 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what happened was they came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were saved again once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what happened was that they really concentrated all the remaining population, legal population, of the ghetto in [POLISH] Street and in the nearby streets.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a kind of cattle kind of encirclement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they then made a selection place, where they were marching everybody out of there, and marching them either left to the Umschlagplatz, or right back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, of course, that went according to their pure ideas of the SS, whom they-- and the children had no chance anyway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the children that survived, they were usually carried in the rucksacks of their parents, or rucksacks, or sacks, or packages, whatever they were carrying, if there were any that-- and, great, so some people, those who were young, and strong, and looked more or less still presentable, were sent back to life.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the rest were sent to Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later, Germans for days, and days, and days, were clearing those blocks of houses, and getting people who were hiding to Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people still saved themselves from [POLISH] Street, although it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that happened, practically the great action was in Warsaw was finished for the time being.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
